    "causal_summary": "The 007 resilience-research packet identified five concrete backend resilience gaps and produced design-ready patch plans for each (iter 8-12 markdowns). This packet (008) lands the actual TypeScript patches that make the live code-graph backend match those design targets. Without this packet the staleness predicate stays mtime-only, the resolver misses cross-file edges through path aliases / type-only imports / re-export barrels, edge weights are unconfigurable, self-healing is invisible to operators, and the gold-battery verification contract from `assets/code-graph-gold-queries.json` has no runtime to execute against.",
